Question: There are exactly two bunches of attached balloons.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://images.freeimages.com/images/premium/large-thumbs/1203/12038329-happy-young-girl-holding-a-bunch-of-balloons-outside.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many bunches of attached balloons are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many bunches of attached balloons are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and {ANSWER1} == 2')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
